SELECT `bu`.`iUserId` AS `bu_blocked_to`,`bu`.`iBlockUserId` AS `bu_blocked_by` FROM `user_block` AS `bu` WHERE (bu.dtAddedAt IS NOT NULL AND bu.dtAddedAt <> '') AND (bu.iUserId = 188 AND bu.iBlockUserId = 183) OR (bu.iUserId = 183 AND bu.iBlockUserId = 188)  LIMIT 1

SELECT `m`.`iMessageId` AS `m_message_id` FROM `message` AS `m` WHERE `m`.`iMessageId` = '199' OR (m.iSenderId IS NOT NULL AND m.iSenderId <> '') AND (m.iSenderId = 188 AND m.iReceiverId = 183) OR (m.iSenderId = 183 AND m.iReceiverId = 188)  LIMIT 1
INSERT INTO `message` (`iMessageId`, `iSenderId`, `iReceiverId`, `vMessage`, `dtAddedDate`, `dtModifiedDate`) VALUES ('199', '188', '183', 'did u tested it', NOW(), NOW())

SELECT `s`.`iUserId` AS `s_users_id`,`r`.`iUserId` AS `r_users_id`,`r`.`vDeviceToken` AS `r_device_token`,CONCAT(s.vFirstName," ",s.vLastName) AS s_name FROM `message` AS `m` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `s` ON `m`.`iSenderId` = `s`.`iUserId` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `r` ON `m`.`iReceiverId` = `r`.`iUserId` WHERE (m.iSenderId = 188 AND m.iReceiverId = 183)  LIMIT 1

SELECT `n`.`iNotificationId` AS `notification_id` FROM `notification` AS `n` WHERE `iSenderId` IN('188') AND `vNotificationmessage` IN('Akash Parmar  has sent you a message.') AND `iReceiverId` IN('183')
